        <div class="reviewText stacked">
              <span id="reviewTextContainer1970559733" class="readable"
              >
            
<span id="freeTextContainer2923962037816573885">Lighthearted romance, with a little more substance than normal for this genre. The main character gets to go to Chicago to the World&apos;s fair and in the process meets several young men and gets to decide what type of life she wants. I liked how the author represented her choices. It was pretty predictable but I enjoyed the read. </span>
  <span id="freeText2923962037816573885" style="display:none">Lighthearted romance, with a little more substance than normal for this genre. The main character gets to go to Chicago to the World's fair and in the process meets several young men and gets to decide what type of life she wants. I liked how the author represented her choices. It was pretty predictable but I enjoyed the read. </span>
  <a data-text-id="2923962037816573885" href="#" onclick="swapContent($(this));; return false;">...more</a>

